**"Investigate the House"** is a text adventure game developed entirely in C# from a **Redmi 9A phone**.  
You are a rookie investigator who must explore a mysterious house and uncover its secrets... including a mysterious antagonist named **Neomar**.

Every decision you make will affect the story and can lead you to different endings.  
